name: SanDiegoGuide
0:
”Alexa, open san diego guide and give me an attraction”
”Alexa, open san diego guide and what are the top five things to do”
”Alexa, open san diego guide and tell me the news”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: san diego guide
des: Are you about to plan your next trip to San Diego, California? If yes, our guide will help you to learn more about this city, various attractions and top five must places to visit here. All attractions include address for navigation and contact information. You can also tune into local San Diego news.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
